# Repo Core Rule

- Follow repository-wide guidance in `AGENTS.md`.
- Respect project boundaries and avoid cross-cutting changes unless requested.
- Preserve testing and coverage gates; do not bypass CI checks.
- Bug fixes require regression tests (fail before, pass after).
- If architecture/testing/release policy changes, sync relevant docs under `docs/`.
